app_name: Groups Control Groups Messenger Apps Snikket
app_description: The Snikket app allows you to join a worldwide communication network. Use the app for communicating with friends family and colleagues without surrendering your data to large corporations. Important Note: To get started with the app you need an invite to a Snikket service or run your own. The app will not work unless you have an invite to join a Snikket service. Snikket allows you to use a service provided by someone you trust. This could be an organisation simply a techie friend or family member. Both the app and service are 100 free and open source software. Questions Browse our FAQ: https: snikket.org app faq
